title: Most Valuable Comic Ever: ‘Superman No. 1’ Sells for a Record $9 Million
summary: The 1939 comic smashed the old record held by Action Comics No. 1, the issue that introduced the Man of Steel.

title: Hollywood’s Secret Beauty Wizards
summary: They won’t come to you. Industry A-Listers go to them. Operating out of unassuming offices, these aesthetic pros to Nicole Kidman and Margot Robbie are best-in-class for antiaging facials, manicures and body waxing.
